data.description: GORGEOUS HOME NESTLED ON 5 PRIVATE ACRES IN CHAPIN, ZONED FOR AWARD WINNING CHAPIN SCHOOLS!MOTIVATED SELLERS! Tired of paying HOA fees and storage fees? This 4 bed/2.5 bath property has an onsite boat/rv covered storage area and is full of amazing features and tons of updates including:NEW ROOF-July 2023! New LVP floor through out the main floor and main 2nd floor hallway-Aug.2023! Exterior pressure wash and window washing of entire house and detached garage Aug 2023! Exterior/interior paint of house and detached garage -Aug 2023! Sod installed (front, back, & side of house)-Sept. 2023! Master bath, wetbar, and laundry room all updated 2022-23! Professional tree service/land clearing of trees surrounding house and detached garage Sept 2023! Professionally steamed cleaned and deodorized all carpet Sept 2023! Natural light spills throughout the flowing layout as you move with ease from one room to the next. The large living room offers a cozy fireplace and easy access to the beautiful wetbar and kitchen! The spacious kitchen boasts tons of counter and cabinet space making cooking a breeze! The huge owner's suite features a 2nd fireplace, sitting area and spa-like en suite with luxurious walk-in shower! Each additional bedroom offers ample closet space and access to lovely shared full bath. The detached 4 car garage makes the perfect place for additional storage or hobbies! Enjoy relaxing on the screened-in porch or deck that look out onto the private, wooded 5 acre property!
